properties.Text:
You currently have no elements.  Press the plus icon in the top-left corner to create a new byt.

A "byt" is what BytExecutor uses to store code that it can run.  Hovering over a byt gives you the primary interactions, such as execute, delete, and others.  Double-click in order to edit a byt.

A more detailed explanation and guide may be found at the Help option or the associated DevForum post.
